Sentencas: A perovskite oxide BixSr1-xCo0.2Fe0.8O3 (BSCF, x = 0.5, 0.6, 0.7) is investigated as a cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performances of BixSr1-xCo0.2Fe0.8O3 (x=0.5, 0.6, 0.7) as Potential Cathode Material for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The BSCF is prepared using solid state reaction method.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performances of BixSr1-xCo0.2Fe0.8O3 (x=0.5, 0.6, 0.7) as Potential Cathode Material for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The XRD shows the perovskite phase is formed at x = 0.5 and impurity phases are detected with x increasing.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performances of BixSr1-xCo0.2Fe0.8O3 (x=0.5, 0.6, 0.7) as Potential Cathode Material for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The area specific resistance value for the BSCF cathode is as low as 0.07 Omega cm(2) at 750 degrees C as x = 0.5.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performances of BixSr1-xCo0.2Fe0.8O3 (x=0.5, 0.6, 0.7) as Potential Cathode Material for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electrolyte-supported fuel cell generates good performance with the peak power densities of 0.078, 0.057, 0.032 Wcm(-2) at 750 degrees C as x = 0.5, 0.6, 0.7, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Performances of BixSr1-xCo0.2Fe0.8O3 (x=0.5, 0.6, 0.7) as Potential Cathode Material for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
